# Contributor Covenant 2.1

## Our Pledge

We pledge to make participation in our project a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Standards

- Empathy, respect, constructive feedback
- No harassment, hate speech, privacy violations

## Enforcement

Report to {{ author }}@users.noreply.github.com. Complaints reviewed within 48h.

